	\nEvent Registration\n\nOn\n\nPrice\n\n$30.00\n\nEmail\n\nJohn@schwager.or
	g\n\nTelephone\n\n206-226-5728\n\nLocation\n\nBellevue Downtown Park\, 102
	01 NE 4th St\, Bellevue\, WA 98004\n\nDescription\n\nAll in for Autism's c
	ause is to raise awareness and funds to support children with Autism Spect
	rum Disorder \\(ASD\\)\, their families\, and caregivers with the ultimate
	 goal of raising their quality of life. Raising a child on the autism spec
	trum can be an exhausting and lonely roller coaster ride. Many families ca
	nnot afford to pay for the services that their autistic children need. Fun
	ds raised from the race will benefit Kindering\, Athletes for Kids\, and o
	ther Rotary projects that benefit children and their families.\n\nJoin us 
	for the 5K \\(run or walk!\\) and the 200m Kids' Dash.\n\n5k Run/Walk cour
	se with fun for the whole family. Dogs welcome. They will have their own s
	pecial bandana for the occasion.\n\nKid's Run - bring the kiddos for a ful
	l family event.\n\nRegister Online\n\nThe\n\nAll in for Autism 5K \, spons
